'''比莉·凱薩琳·洛爾德'''（{{lang-en|Billie Catherine Lourd}}，{{bd|1992年|7月17日|||catIdx=L}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://birth-records.mooseroots.com/l/37702650/Billie-Catherine-Lourd|title=Billie Lourd California, Birth Index, 1905–1995 – FamilySearch|first=|last=|date=January 26, 2015|accessdate=January 26, 2015|publisher=Mooseroots}}</ref>），[[美國|美國]][[女演員|女演員]]。知名作品為Fox頻道播出的《[[尖叫女王|尖叫女王]]》，飾演香奈兒3號。

== 生平 ==
洛爾德誕生於美國[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]。洛爾德有英格蘭、蘇格蘭、威爾士、蘇格蘭-愛爾蘭人/北愛爾蘭人、德國、法國和[[猶太|猶太]]血統<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm6609666/bio|title=Billie Lourd - Biography|work=IMDb|accessdate=2018-06-21|archive-date=2017-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171111022018/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm6609666/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/obituaries/eddie-fisher-singer-and-actor-whose-career-was-overshadowed-by-his-marriages-and-divorces-2089140.html|title=Eddie Fisher: Singer and actor whose career was overshadowed by his marriages and divorces|last=Riley|first=John|date=September 25, 2010|work=The Independent|accessdate=June 22, 2018|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327090116/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/obituaries/eddie-fisher-singer-and-actor-whose-career-was-overshadowed-by-his-marriages-and-divorces-2089140.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/2495790/eddie-fisher-father-carrie-fisher-husband-debbie-reynolds-elizabeth-taylor-memorial/|title=Who is Eddie Fisher? Father of Carrie Fisher and ex-husband of Debbie Reynolds - here's what we know|last=Littlejohn|first=Georgina|date=March 24, 2017|work=The Sun|accessdate=June 22, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622060334/https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/2495790/eddie-fisher-father-carrie-fisher-husband-debbie-reynolds-elizabeth-taylor-memorial/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。洛爾德的外祖父[[艾迪·費雪|艾迪·費雪]]是猶太人<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.interfaithfamily.com/arts_and_entertainment/popular_culture/hollywood_now_new_roles_for_jlaw_ben_stiller_and_more/|title=Hollywood Now: New Roles for JLaw, Ben Stiller and More|accessdate=June 21, 2018|date=September 6, 2017|last=Miller|first=Gerri|work=InterfaithFamily.com|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622024903/https://www.interfaithfamily.com/arts_and_entertainment/popular_culture/hollywood_now_new_roles_for_jlaw_ben_stiller_and_more/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.vanityfair.com/style/2016/12/carrie-fisher-parents-debbie-reynolds-eddie-hollywood|title=Inside Carrie Fisher’s Difficult Upbringing with Famous Parents|last=Miller|first=Julie|date=December 27, 2016|work=Vanity Fair|accessdate=June 22, 2018|archive-date=2017-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117125049/https://www.vanityfair.com/style/2016/12/carrie-fisher-parents-debbie-reynolds-eddie-hollywood|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2010/sep/24/eddie-fisher-obituary|title=Eddie Fisher obituary|accessdate=June 22, 2018|date=September 24, 2010|last=Freedland|first=Michael|work=The Guardian|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622140109/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2010/sep/24/eddie-fisher-obituary|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1648615/eddie-fisher-singer-and-ex-of-elizabeth-taylor-dies/|title=Eddie Fisher, Singer And Ex Of Elizabeth Taylor, Dies|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|date=September 24, 2010|work=MTV News|accessdate=June 22, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622111443/http://www.mtv.com/news/1648615/eddie-fisher-singer-and-ex-of-elizabeth-taylor-dies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她是女演員[[嘉莉·費雪|嘉莉·費雪]]以及[[人才中介|人才中介]]{{tsl|en|Bryan Lourd|布萊恩·盧德}}之女<ref name="Interview 2015-06">{{cite web |last=Kelsey |first=Colleen |title=Film: Billie Lourd |url=http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/billie-lourd/# |work=[[Interview_(magazine)|Interview]] |date=June 8, 2015 |accessdate=December 14, 2015 |archive-date=2015-06-10 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20150610010718/http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/billie-lourd/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="DM 2014-06">{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2674870/Carrie-Fishers-daughter-Billie-Lourd-play-young-Princess-Leia-Star-Wars-Episode-VII.html |title=Carrie Fisher's daughter Billie Lourd, 21, to play young Princess Leia in ''Star Wars: Episode VII'' |work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]] |first=Jason |last=Chester |date=June 20, 2015 |accessdate=October 25, 2015 |archive-date=2016-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110215221/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2674870/Carrie-Fishers-daughter-Billie-Lourd-play-young-Princess-Leia-Star-Wars-Episode-VII.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。洛爾德也是女演員[[黛比·雷諾|黛比·雷諾]]和歌手[[艾迪·費雪|艾迪·費雪]]的孫女、{{tsl|en|Todd Fisher|陶德·費雪}}、{{tsl|en|Joely Fisher|喬莉·費雪}}以及{{tsl|en|Tricia Leigh Fisher|崔西亞·莉·費雪}}的姪女。她也是[[艾瑪·羅勃茲|艾瑪·羅勃茲]]的兒時玩伴。

洛爾德在[[紐約大學|紐約大學]]學習[[宗教學|宗教學]]以及[[心理學|心理學]]，並於2014年畢業<ref name="Interview 2015-06"/>。

2016年，她與《[[尖叫女王|尖叫女王]]》同劇演員[[泰勒·洛納|泰勒·洛納]]開始交往。-{洛納}-在盧德接連失去母親與祖母的時候都陪著她度過。另外，《[[尖叫女王|尖叫女王]]》的[[潔美·李·寇蒂斯|潔美·李·寇蒂斯]]、[[艾碧·貝絲琳|艾碧·貝絲琳]]、[[亞莉安娜·格蘭德|亞莉安娜·格蘭德]]、[[麗婭·米雪兒|麗婭·米雪兒]]、[[葛倫·鮑威爾|葛倫·鮑威爾]]及[[約翰·史坦摩斯|約翰·史坦摩斯]]也在這段時間為洛爾德打氣。在沈默了一段之後，她於Instagram上發文表達對母親及祖母的哀悼與思念並感謝人們對她們的祝福。

2017年，洛爾德與[[泰勒·洛納|泰勒·洛納]]分手<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://people.com/movies/billie-lourd-taylor-lautner-split/|title=Billie Lourd and Taylor Lautner Break Up After 8 Months Together: 'They Are Still Friendly,' Says Source|last=Russian|first=Ale|date=July 6, 2017|work=People Magazine|accessdate=June 22, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622140230/https://people.com/movies/billie-lourd-taylor-lautner-split/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 職業生活 ==
2014年6月，[[太陽報_(英國)|太陽報]]報導洛爾德將會出現在[[星際大戰|星際大戰]]系列續集電影《[[STAR_WARS：原力覺醒|STAR WARS：原力覺醒]]》，飾演年輕版的[[莉亞公主|莉亞公主]]，也是其母[[嘉莉·費雪|嘉莉·費雪]]飾演的角色<ref name="DM 2014-06"/>2015年5月洛爾德表示她在電影中將會飾演康妮克斯<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.etonline.com/movies/164311_carrie_fisher_s_daughter_billie_lourd_confirms_she_s_not_young_princess_leia_the_force_awakens/ |title=Carrie Fisher’s Daughter Billie Lourd Confirms She’s Not Young Princess Leia in ''The Force Awakens'' |work=[[Entertainment_Tonight|Entertainment Tonight]] |first=Ashley |last=Crossan |date=May 11, 2015 |accessdate=October 25, 2015 |archive-date=2016-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101050640/http://www.etonline.com/movies/164311_carrie_fisher_s_daughter_billie_lourd_confirms_she_s_not_young_princess_leia_the_force_awakens/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 或是莉亞之女<ref name="Interview 2015-06"/>。 

2015年2月，洛爾德參演Fox頻道播出的喜劇恐怖影集《[[尖叫女王|尖叫女王]]》。<ref name="DL Scream 1">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/02/billie-lourd-cast-scream-queens-fox-1201365095/ |title=Billie Lourd Joins Fox’s ''Scream Queens'' |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |date=February 2, 2015 |accessdate=October 25, 2015 |archive-date=2017-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217044745/http://deadline.com/2015/02/billie-lourd-cast-scream-queens-fox-1201365095/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 洛爾德的角色是一個富有的姊妹會-{少女}-香奈兒3號，她穿戴耳罩是向原版《[[星際大戰|星際大戰]]》電影系列中[[嘉莉·費雪|嘉莉·費雪]]的致敬<ref name="USA Today">{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2015/09/25/carrie-fishers-daughter-dons-leia-like-earmuffs-scream-queens/72824768/ |title=The royal reason for ''Scream Queens'' earmuffs |work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |first=Hoai-Tran |last=Bui |date=September 25, 2015 |accessdate=October 25, 2015 |archive-date=2017-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170126112749/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2015/09/25/carrie-fishers-daughter-dons-leia-like-earmuffs-scream-queens/72824768/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BuzzFeed">{{cite web |url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/jarettwieselman/reason-behind-those-earmuffs-on-scream-queens# |title=Princess Leia’s Daughter Is Reprising That Iconic ''Star Wars'' Look |publisher=[[BuzzFeed|BuzzFeed]] |first=Jarett |last=Wieselman |date=September 25, 2015 |accessdate=October 25, 2015 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220033540/https://www.buzzfeed.com/jarettwieselman/reason-behind-those-earmuffs-on-scream-queens |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

2015年12月，[[Variety|Variety]]報導洛爾德與《[[尖叫女王|尖叫女王]]》同劇演員[[艾瑪·羅勃茲|艾瑪·羅勃茲]]加入傳記犯罪劇情電影《億萬男孩俱樂部》 ，在劇中飾演羅珊娜<ref name="bbclub">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/billie-lourd-bokeem-woodbine-jeremy-irvine-billionaire-boys-club-1201662176/ |title=Billie Lourd, Bokeem Woodbine, Jeremy Irvine Join ''Billionaire Boys Club'' (EXCLUSIVE) |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |first=Dave |last=McNary |date=December 15, 2015 |accessdate=December 15, 2015 |archive-date=2017-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106110835/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/billie-lourd-bokeem-woodbine-jeremy-irvine-billionaire-boys-club-1201662176/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年1月，[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]報導洛爾德將會回歸《尖叫女王》第二季<ref name="DL Scream 2">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/scream-queens-season-2-cast-lea-michele-emma-roberts-abigail-breslin-keke-palmer-1201684132/ |title=''Scream Queens'': Who Is Coming Back For Season 2? |publisher=Deadline.com |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |date=January 15, 2016 |accessdate=January 20, 2016 |archive-date=2016-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110125048/http://deadline.com/2016/01/scream-queens-season-2-cast-lea-michele-emma-roberts-abigail-breslin-keke-palmer-1201684132/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年，洛爾德將繼續在《[[STAR_WARS：最後的絕地武士|STAR WARS：最後的絕地武士]]》飾演康妮克斯。

